# JavaScript Usage

This project uses **JavaScript only in every folder except contracts** - do not use TypeScript.
exception: contracts folder 

## Guidelines

- Use `.js` file extensions for all JavaScript files
- Use `.jsx` file extensions for React components
- Do not create `.ts` or `.tsx` files
- Use JSDoc comments for type documentation when needed
- Focus on modern JavaScript (ES6+) features
